criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

  -  adult patients >=18 years of age;

  -  diagnosis of systemic lupus erythematosus and lupus nephritis (class III, IV or V).

Exclusion Criteria:

  -  patients who have received cytotoxic drugs in previous 8 weeks;

  -  systemic infections;

  -  hepatitis B or C, or HIV.
